mitonize.datastore

クラス LZFCompressor

  • java.lang.Object
    • mitonize.datastore.Compressor
      • mitonize.datastore.LZFCompressor

  • public class LZFCompressor
extends Compressor
    Compress payload with LZF algorithm. LZF compression algorithm, written in Java, is much faster than Deflater and Inflater, but compressed size is larger about 40-50% than that by them.
    導入されたバージョン:
    1.0.7
    関連項目:
    https://github.com/ning/compress
